Global Constraints

No API credentials in logs: All error messages mask {broker}_api_key, vault operations, LLM API keys
Broker rate limits: ccxt always enableRateLimit=True; httpx always timeout=30.0
WebSocket local-only: No remote auth required (matches existing design)
Paper trading isolation: Each agent has paper_trading_balance in DB; no shared simulation state
Approval gate non-blocking: Human-in-loop trades don't block scheduler; pending approval stored in-memory dict
Confidence formula immutable: Hardcoded in confidence_scorer.py, only unit tested


